> 
> space after comma.
> 
> Odd indentation here.  Use tabs, no spaces.
> 
> > +	    (*str)++;
> > +	    upper_range = simple_strtol ((*str), NULL, 0);
> 
> No space after function name.
> 
> > +	    inc_counter = upper_range - *pint ;
